{"tid":1879503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[政府上訴成功］政府總部東翼前地限制市民進出的做法無違憲","createTime":"2020-02-14T08:41:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T10:26:41.000Z","uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"edfe393852ec6c4c9bfdfba2b40eff55e2322890","tid":1879503,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T08:41:26.000Z","msg":"上訴庭的判詞指出，政府是政府總部業權擁有人，在法律授權下設立合理的使用場地機制，而公眾可無障礙申請，相關的限制有合法目的，不認同原審法官區慶祥所指，政府以業主身分限制市民集會同表達自由犯了法律上錯誤。<br />\n<br />\n上訴庭同意東翼前地設計原意並非作示威之用，行政署署長作為管理人，有責任確保東翼前地運作正常，照顧政總內員工，若政府失責亦會負上民事責任。<br />\n<br />\n上訴庭認為行政署施加的限制，已在管理及集會表達自由之間取得平衡，認為原審法官區慶祥裁決有錯，推翻違憲裁決。<br />\n<br />\n上訴庭認為行政署施加的限制，已在管理及集會表達自由之間取得平衡，認為原審法官區慶祥裁決有錯，推翻違憲裁決。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=380589&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D380589%26refer%3DShare&d=NEgIrN0XKBZxjsPVzjJKR2WYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=a50e78e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D380589%26refer%3DShare&h=083e48e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=380589&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"203897da866e737435f91586a3d700dab031fc9e","tid":1879503,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:19:16.000Z","msg":"搞錯，去唔去終審"},{"pid":"c54a7eba314e841bd875e0ae334467103dcf7d46","tid":1879503,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:16:06.000Z","msg":"哈，popo就沖入邊度都得，私人地方都變非法集結"},{"pid":"5d349fb2717101b4dd1850d5cbc1ed6c57b73836","tid":1879503,"uid":40520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:26:41.000Z","msg":"大狀黨：我唔知 連登仔投票比我就贏<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8jHRCLa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8jHRCLa.gif&h=d7989a14&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}